headline: 3 Reasons to Sell GL and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Globe Life has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 7.1%. Its stock price has climbed to $139.10, representing a healthy 13.5% increase. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
